OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772561166
OL,3,C19th Century human remains reburied
OL,4,Cafter find by gas pipe workers
OL,6,FThe remains of several people from the
OL,7,F19th Century have been reburied in
OL,8,FStockport after they were unearthed
OL,9,Fduring gas pipeline works.
OL,11,FWorkers from gas distribution firm
OL,12,FCadent called police after discovering
OL,13,Fthe bones while diverting an
OL,14,Funderground pipe, last May, as part of
OL,15,Frebuilding a bridge over the main West
OL,16,FCoast railway line.
OL,18,FOfficers from Greater Manchester
OL,19,FPolice determined the bones, found on
OL,20,FShaw Heath, had "likely been there for
OL,21,Fa considerable amount of time."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
