PN,39702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772561166
OL,3,C19th Century human remains reburied
OL,4,Cafter find by gas pipe workers
OL,6,FArchaeologists examined the site and
OL,7,Fconfirmed the bones were those of 14
OL,8,Fpeople - seven adults, one teenager
OL,9,Fand six children under the age of
OL,10,Fthree.
OL,12,FA church had stood on the spot in the
OL,13,F1800s, with burials taking place until
OL,14,F1856. The building was demolished in
OL,15,F1911 and surviving records in "poor
OL,16,Fcondition" gave no clue as to who the
OL,17,Fburied people were.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
