FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772561166
OL,3,C19th Century human remains reburied
OL,4,Cafter find by gas pipe workers
OL,6,FPrincipal Archaeologist Megan Stoakley
OL,7,Fsaid: "This was an unusual case for
OL,8,Four team. We didn't begin with intact
OL,9,Fgraves.
OL,11,F"Instead, we encountered
OL,12,Fdisarticulated remains in ground
OL,13,Fdisturbed long after the original
OL,14,Fburials.
OL,16,F"Piece by piece, we've rebuilt the
OL,17,Fsite's story and ensured a dignified
OL,18,Freburial."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
