FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772561166
OL,3,C19th Century human remains reburied
OL,4,Cafter find by gas pipe workers
OL,6,FMs Stoakley added that Stockport's
OL,7,Fovercrowded and poor housing, during
OL,8,Fthe industrial revolution, led to high
OL,9,Fmortality rates - particularly among
OL,10,Fchildren.
OL,12,FThe 14 people were reburied at the
OL,13,Ftown's Park Road Cemetery.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
